window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Are men literally born to cheat? Does monogamy actually serve women's interests? These are among the questions that have made <i>The Moral Animal</i> one of the most provocative science books in recent years. Wright unveils the genetic strategies behind everything from our sexual preferences to our office politics - as well as their implications for our moral codes and public policies.</p>"; 
